# Credentials (gitignored — copy to docs/CREDENTIALS.md when seeded)

> This file is the example. The real one (`docs/CREDENTIALS.md`) is gitignored.
> Phase 02 seeds the super-admin. Update this file after running `npm run db:seed:admin`.

## Local dev

- **Admin URL:** http://localhost:3000/admin
- **Login URL:** http://localhost:3000/login
- **Super-admin email:** admin@example.com
- **Super-admin password:** (set via `INITIAL_ADMIN_PASSWORD` in `.env.local`)
- **MongoDB Compass URI:** `mongodb://admin:devpassword@localhost:27018/myportfolio?authSource=admin`
- _(host port 27018 → container port 27017 to avoid colliding with a host-installed mongod)_
- **Mongo Express UI:** http://localhost:8081 (admin / devpassword)

## Production

- Cluster: MongoDB Atlas free tier — connection string in Vercel env `MONGODB_URI`.
